OL,3,C60-year-old lands #500 court bill for
OL,4,Ccycling in pedestrianised area
OL,6,FA 60-year-old man has been hit with a
OL,7,Flegal bill of more than #500 for
OL,8,Fcycling through a pedestrianised area
OL,9,Fof a town centre.
OL,11,FAndrew Billingham was found guilty of
OL,12,Fbreaching a public space protection
OL,13,Forder (PSPO), designed to combat
OL,14,Fnuisance behaviour, by riding along
OL,15,FVictoria Street in Grimsby.
OL,17,FHe refused to pay an initial fine,
OL,18,Fclaiming he had dismounted before
OL,19,Fentering Victoria Street.
