OL,6,FBut he was convicted at Grimsby
OL,7,FMagistrates Court and fined #200 and
OL,8,Fordered to pay #250 in costs and a
OL,9,Fvictim surcharge of #80.
OL,11,FCllr Ron Shepherd said: "It's
OL,12,Fimportant that people understand the
OL,13,Frules across North East Lincolnshire
OL,14,Fand adhere to them.
OL,16,F"Our council plan advocates a zero-
OL,17,Ftolerance policy and we constantly
OL,18,Freview how we deliver our enforcement
OL,19,Fto make sure we can effectively tackle
OL,20,Fany issues."
