OL,3,C60-year-old lands #500 court bill for
OL,4,Ccycling in pedestrianised area
OL,6,FGrimsby became one of a number of
OL,7,Ftowns to impose a cycling ban in
OL,8,Fpedestrianised zones in 2019.
OL,10,FIt was designed to deal with nuisance
OL,11,Fbehaviour in the town centre and along
OL,12,FCleethorpes seafront.
OL,14,FThe order was extended in July and
OL,15,Fwill now last until 2025. More than
OL,16,F1,000 fixed penalty notices have been
OL,17,Fissued since 2019, the bulk of which
OL,18,Fhave been for cycling on Victoria
OL,19,FStreet South and walking dogs along
OL,20,Fthe main beach.
